  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>How To Mine</h1>
  </div>
  <p class="lead">In order to mine on this pool you need to have an
    <a href="https://github.com/ethereum/webthree-umbrella/releases" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">ethminer</a> installation
    pointed to<br/><code>{{config.HttpHost}}:{{config.HttpPort}}/YOUR_BLACK_ADDRESS/RIG_ID</code>
  </p>
  <dl class="dl-horizontal">
    <dt>YOUR_BLACK_ADDRESS</dt>
    <dd>This is your address for payouts, generate one with gblack or
      <a href="" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">MetaMask</a>.<br/>
      <strong>Example:</strong> <code>0xb85150eb365e7df0941f0cf08235f987ba91506a</code>.
    </dd>
    <dt>RIG_ID</dt>
    <dd>
      ID of your farm to distinguish it from your other rig. If you have just one rig, feel free to omit this param.
      This param must be short alphanumeric string with optional dashes and underscores.<br/>
      <strong>Example:</strong> <code>rig-1</code>
    </dd>
  </dl>
  <p>
    <strong>Full example:</strong>
    <code>ethminer -F {{config.HttpHost}}:{{config.HttpPort}}/0xb85150eb365e7df0941f0cf08235f987ba91506a/myfarm -G --farm-recheck 200</code>.<br/>
    <span class="label label-info">Hint:</span> If you are compiling ethminer from latest source, please also use
      extra <code>--disable-submit-hashrate</code> option.
  </p>

  <h4>Stratum Mining with ClaymoreMiner for BlackChain</h4>
  <p class="lead">Download miner for GPU <a href="https://github.com/black-networks/claymoreminer" re="nofollow" target="_blank">Claymore Miner Github</a>.</p>
  <p class="lead">Edit <code>black-gpu.bat</code> and enter your <code>WALLET</code>.</p>


